 Pizza photo pizzaneeds.com Pizza is a unique cuisine that is both nutritious and appropriate for all kinds of occasions. Pizza is an Italian dish consisting of a round, flattened dough base baked with a tomato and cheese topping, usually with additional meat, fish, or vegetables. This savory dish, as well as its variations, has gained popularity and acceptance in many parts of the world. Pizza is a popular fast food item that is available fresh or frozen, whole or in portions. Despite being a fast food, the fun part is that it can be made at home; the dough can be made ahead of time and even frozen, and any toppings may be used to fit one’s taste buds. Pizza is easier to make than you might imagine. With this recipe you might just be  making pizza that rivals some of the greatest you are used to ordering. To make a great pizza, you’ll need good dough, tomato ketchup/ self made  sauce, toppings, and cheese. You can add whatever other components you like. This flat yummy meal is popular among children and adults. INGREDIENTS METHOD Enjoy